metadata.rawOutput:
{
  "markdown_content": "# 谢谢款待\n\n## 1. 英文:\n- **翻译**: Thank you for your hospitality\n- **解释**: An expression of gratitude for the kindness and generosity shown by someone who has provided food, drink, or entertainment.\n- **例句1**: Thank you for your hospitality during my stay.\n  - 谢谢您在我逗留期间提供的款待。\n- **例句2**: I really appreciate the warm welcome and hospitality you offered us.\n  - 我们非常感激您给予我们的热情接待和款待。\n\n## 2. 日本語:\n- **翻訳**: ご馳走様でした\n- **解説**: 食事や飲み物、娯楽を提供してくださった方への感謝の言葉。\n- **例句1**: ご馳走様でした。\n  - 谢谢款待。\n- **例句2**: おもてなしに感謝します。\n  - 感谢您的款待。\n\n## 3. 中文:\n- **翻译**: 谢谢款待\n- **解释**: 对于主人提供的食物、饮料或娱乐表示感谢的话。",
  "audio_tasks": [
    {
      "text": "Thank you for your hospitality during my stay.",
      "lang": "en",
      "filename_suffix": "_en_1"
    },
    {
      "text": "I really appreciate the warm welcome and hospitality you offered us.",
      "lang": "en",
      "filename_suffix": "_en_2"
    },
    {
      "text": "ご馳走様でした。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "filename_suffix": "_ja_1"
    },
    {
      "text": "おもてなしに感謝します。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "filename_suffix": "_ja_2"
    }
  ]
}

